Module org.apache.jena.permissions
Package org.apache.jena.permissions.query.rewriter

Class OpRewriter

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.permissions.query.rewriter.OpRewriter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.jena.sparql.algebra.OpVisitor
public class OpRewriter extends Object implements org.apache.jena.sparql.algebra.OpVisitor
This class rewrites the query by examining each operation in the algebra returned by the Jena SPARQL parser.

This implementation inserts security evaluator checks where necessary.
